         <abstract id="aspace_3cf7591ab55782fd241f55c7f0254d95">The collection contains research, publications, pamphlets, and mimeographed papers concerning the ethnic conflict and democracy in Suriname during the decades of the 1960s and mid-1970s.</abstract>
