      <scopecontent id="aspace_2f50ad6bac616799ae90fb243d649b56">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection contains research, publications, pamphlets, and mimeographed papers concerning the ethnic conflict and democracy in Suriname during the decades of the 1960s and mid-1970s.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_39cc2276bcd19358e07ce2e045c6dc33">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_1189866e6bd8b21ad767a1a12900e1a5">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Edward M. Dew III Collection on Suriname (MS 2064). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_2fc7460b25358026cdd56720d708b94e">
